com.strongloop.android.loopback

Class ModelPrototype<T extends Model>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.strongloop.android.remoting.Prototype
      • com.strongloop.android.loopback.ModelPrototype<T>

  • public class ModelPrototype<T extends Model>
extends Prototype
    A local representative of a single model type on the server, encapsulating the name of the model type for easy Model creation, discovery, and management.
